Before it came due, his father purchased the loan through the newly created D B Pace Acquisition. The senior Trump promptly foreclosed, accepting the value of the property as his payment. Titan Atlas Manufacturing reportedly left "a trail of litigation, unpaid bills and unpaid taxes" in its wake. It was a successort to the similarly named Titan Atlast Global, which also failed.Donald Trump Jr.Titan Atlas ManufacturingpotentialThe Post and CourierJan 18, 2016
